                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4494" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1133</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8331 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“几易战略”到名扬奥斯卡—阿里影业的波折之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Changing Strategy to famous Oscar—The twists and turns of Alibaba pictures</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佘震宇，倪子砚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿里巴巴影业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿里影业；互联网影视；公司战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Alibaba Pictures; Corporate Strategy; Internet video</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年2月25日，第91届奥斯卡金像奖各大奖项颁出，电影《绿皮书》荣膺最佳男配角、最佳原创剧本、最佳影片三项大奖，而阿里影业作为其背后的中国资本更让人惊叹，阿里影业也成为全球首家联合出品奥斯卡最佳影片的互联网影视公司。回顾过去两年的中国电影市场，《战狼2》《芳华》《我不是药神》《西虹市首富》《流浪地球》等等爆款电影背后，阿里影业的地位都值得一提。这时我们不禁都有疑问，为什么阿里影业每次都能抓住机会？本案例希望通过对阿里影业发展历程的描述，梳理其一路走来的战略规划，引导学员进行公司战略分析，思考使其能够从众多影业公司中凸显出来的原因，深入理解企业战略管理相关问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On February 25, 2019, the 91st Academy Awards were presented. The film &quot;Green Paper&quot; won the Best Supporting Actor, Best Original Screenplay and Best Film Awards, and Ali Films as its The Chinese capital behind it is even more amazing. Ali Pictures has also become the world&#39;s first Internet film company to jointly produce the best films of Oscar. Looking back at the Chinese film market in the past two years, behind the explosion of &quot;War Wolf 2&quot;, &quot;Fanghua&quot;, &quot;I am not a drug god&quot;, &quot;Xihong City&#39;s richest man&quot;, &quot;Wandering Earth&quot; and so on, the status of Ali Pictures is worth mentioning. At this time we can&#39;t help but have questions. Why does Ali Cinema seize the opportunity every time? This case hopes to sort out the strategic plan of Ali&#39;s development through the description of the development process of Alibaba Pictures, guide the students to carry out the company&#39;s strategic analysis, and think about the reasons that can be highlighted from many film companies, and deeply understand the strategic management of enterprises. problem.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
